ack\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ikq1665702951085.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ikq1665702951085.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ikq1665702951085.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ikq1665702951085\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Database Access on MySQL\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__database_access_on_mysql_161230\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The MQL connector uses the MySQL client library to connect to the server and\n      manipulate the DBMS.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__topic_d35637e1_d35638e1_d35639e1_d35640e1_d35641e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1192104e53\">\n                        \n Logon Information\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__p_d53930e1_d53931e1_d53932e1\">In the assignment file, specify the connector and database path:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS]MQL = <var class=\"keyword varname\">Version</var> ; for example MQL=U5.0\n                          [PATHS]$MQL MQL:<var class=\"keyword varname\">HostId</var>{+<var class=\"keyword varname\">Port</var>}:{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Database</var>}|{<var class=\"keyword varname\">UserName</var>}|{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var>}\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__p_d53933e1_d53934e1_d53935e1\">The default port is 3306. If you want to use a different port, explicitly specify <var class=\"keyword varname\">Port</var>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__topic_d35642e1_d35643e1_d35644e1_d35645e1_d35646e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1192104e90\">\n                        \n Close and Open Support\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__p_d53939e1_d53940e1_d53941e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">open</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">close</span> instructions are fully supported. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">open</span> instruction opens the relevant path and attempts to log on to the database. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">close</span> instruction closes all tables and logs off from MySQL, shutting down that path.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__topic_d35647e1_d35648e1_d35649e1_d35650e1_d35651e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1192104e111\">\n                        \n Using MySQL for the Repository\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikq1665702951085__p_d53945e1_d53946e1_d53947e1\">MySQL Server can be used for the Uniface Repository. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mfn1665702736511.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mfn1665702736511.html\" title=\"The application data that is modeled by database entities in the IDE must be stored in a database that matches the modeled definitions.\">Generate Scripts for Creating Database Tables</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lnl1665702774754.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Access</a><p>Uniface automatically opens the DBMS when a read or write ProcScript statement is issued. The path and logon details for the specific database (or databases) can be provided in an assignment file, a command line instruction, or in the open ProcScript instruction.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sbg1665702735473.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Paths and Path Assignments</a><p>A path is a named route to a resource required by the application, such as a database connector and database, a remote server, or a file location.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database Access on MySQL Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Database Access on MySQL The MQL connector uses the MySQL client library to connect to the server and manipulate the DBMS. Logon Information In the assignment file, specify the connector and database path: [DRIVER_SETTINGS]MQL = Version ; for example MQL=U5.0 [PATHS]$MQL MQL: HostId {+ Port }:{ Database }|{ UserName }|{ Password } Copy The default port is 3306. If you want to use a different port, explicitly specify Port . Close and Open Support The open and close instructions are fully supported. The open instruction opens the relevant path and attempts to log on to the database. The close instruction closes all tables and logs off from MySQL, shutting down that path. Using MySQL for the Repository MySQL Server can be used for the Uniface Repository. For more information, see Generate Scripts for Creating Database Tables . Related Links Database Access Uniface automatically opens the DBMS when a read or write ProcScript statement is issued. The path and logon details for the specific database (or databases) can be provided in an assignment file, a command line instruction, or in the open ProcScript instruction. Paths and Path Assignments A path is a named route to a resource required by the application, such as a database connector and database, a remote server, or a file location. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}